Vampyres are monsters which may be found fighting for Zamorak in the God Wars Dungeon. They are slightly stronger than their Morytanian counterparts, but lack the immunity to non-silver and blisterwood weapons that most vampyres have. Moreover, when attacked by a player wearing a holy symbol, they will receive a 25% reduction to their attack and defence.
